Create an ‘about’ session in your project, it could be a pop-up info panel or an individual web page. Write a 150-200 word description of your project in the ‘about’ session. The description should include your thoughts on what (is this project), why (is it important), who (are you creating the website for), how(is this project responding to certain social justice issues). Also, please include the description in your README.md file.

Box layout (thanks-info): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I4mD0dft2Yo
Popup tutorial (thanks-info): https://www.w3schools.com/howto/howto_js_fullscreen_overlay.asp
Button code (#button #button1): https://www.w3schools.com/css/tryit.asp?filename=trycss_buttons_hover
